Karena kamu kaya, belilah sepuluh buku.

796
00:38:48,489 --> 00:38:50,429
- Berapa harganya?
- Sembilan puluh dolar.

797
00:38:52,460 --> 00:38:54,069
- Bisa bayar pake kartu?
- Tentu saja.

798
00:38:54,869 --> 00:38:57,439
